1
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:30,560
Then how are you going to compensate?

2
00:00:30,730 --> 00:00:33,560
My good disciple, it's up to you.

3
00:00:36,130 --> 00:00:37,560
How much do they owe you?

4
00:00:37,830 --> 00:00:39,160
Just say it.

5
00:00:40,730 --> 00:00:41,790
Thank you, Master.

6
00:00:42,230 --> 00:00:45,160
I guarded the Heavenly Abyss for the Taixuan Holy Land for 300 years,

7
00:00:45,160 --> 00:00:49,330
and killed 32.8 million high-level demonic beasts.

8
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:52,700
Calculated according to the market price of the highest demonic beast bounty in Zhongzhou,

9
00:00:52,700 --> 00:00:56,430
your sect owes me a total of four billion top-grade spirit stones.

10
00:00:58,660 --> 00:00:59,360
How much?

11
00:01:00,130 --> 00:01:03,160
Four billion top-grade spirit stones?

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,600
The cultivation expenses for ordinary disciples like us for a year

13
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,330
is only a dozen top-grade spirit stones.

14
00:01:07,330 --> 00:01:12,060
Four billion, this is enough for the Taixuan Holy Land to spend for hundreds of years.

15
00:01:12,100 --> 00:01:12,830
What?

16
00:01:13,660 --> 00:01:14,760
You want to deny your debt?

17
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:15,820
I don't believe it.

18
00:01:15,900 --> 00:01:18,260
How could you alone kill so many demonic beasts?

19
00:01:18,260 --> 00:01:20,920
Summon the Taixuan Heart-Questioning Mirror.

20
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:29,430
The Heavenly Abyss is filled with demonic miasma,

21
00:01:29,430 --> 00:01:31,430
and the demonic beasts are extremely fierce.

22
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:35,229
This child could actually guard such a dangerous place for 300 years

23
00:01:35,229 --> 00:01:37,690
and kill tens of millions of demonic beasts.

24
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:40,560
Such a genius wants to leave the sect,

25
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:44,100
and you idiots actually agreed.

26
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:45,960
Please calm down, Patriarch.

27
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:48,229
Yao'er has an unprecedented Flying Immortal Physique.

28
00:01:48,229 --> 00:01:49,700
She will definitely become an immortal in the future.

29
00:01:49,700 --> 00:01:52,830
Our Taixuan must exhaust all resources to help her grow.

30
00:01:52,860 --> 00:01:56,600
If hostile forces know that the revival of our Taixuan Cauldron is restrained,

31
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,300
they will surely take advantage of it.

32
00:01:58,300 --> 00:02:00,600
Our Taixuan will face a devastating disaster.

33
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:02,300
Let's just pay to avoid trouble.

34
00:02:02,300 --> 00:02:03,300
Okay.

35
00:02:04,200 --> 00:02:05,700
We will compensate.

36
00:02:07,260 --> 00:02:11,060
Fellow Daoist, can you put away the Imperial Weapon now?

37
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,960
I hate fighting the most.

38
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:17,630
It would be best if we could make peace over a drink.

39
00:02:23,600 --> 00:02:25,400
Master is the best.

40
00:02:26,230 --> 00:02:28,160
So much money.

41
00:02:29,360 --> 00:02:30,360
What a loser.

42
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:32,660
It's over.

43
00:02:32,660 --> 00:02:33,960
No fight.

44
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:37,960
Why doesn't the old demon Gu Linyuan stay quietly in the Eastern Wasteland?

45
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:40,400
Why did he come to the Taixuan Holy Land to snatch people?

46
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,300
Who knows.

47
00:02:41,660 --> 00:02:43,300
But it seems that before he left,

48
00:02:43,300 --> 00:02:47,100
this old demon extorted four billion spirit stones from the Taixuan Holy Land,

49
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:49,500
and the Taixuan Holy Lord even got slapped.

50
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:55,660
This old demon is so arrogant.

51
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:58,500
Wandering around carrying an Extreme Dao Imperial Weapon.

52
00:02:58,500 --> 00:03:00,830
Oh no, is this guy running out of lifespan?

53
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,500
Knowing that breaking through the Emperor Realm is hopeless,

54
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:03,830
an ominous event happened in his twilight years,

55
00:03:03,830 --> 00:03:06,630
so he brought the Extreme Dao Imperial Weapon out to frantically collect wealth.

56
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:10,760
Makes sense. We can't afford to offend a Quasi-Emperor who went mad in his twilight years.

57
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,530
Run away quickly.

58
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:21,560
Congratulations to the host for receiving the gratitude of the villainess Ji Qingchen.

59
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:22,460
Favorability increased.

60
00:03:22,460 --> 00:03:24,900
The current Destiny Luck Points are over 2,000.

61
00:03:24,900 --> 00:03:26,960
It's enough for me to break through directly to the late stage of the Great Emperor Realm.

62
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:27,730
But no rush.

63
00:03:27,829 --> 00:03:29,060
Let's lie low for a while longer.

64
00:03:29,060 --> 00:03:30,260
When those people from the Immortal Realm come down,

65
00:03:30,260 --> 00:03:31,460
I'll give them a surprise.

66
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:32,630
Master.

67
00:03:33,500 --> 00:03:35,460
Why are you protecting me like this today?

68
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:36,660
In my past life memory,

69
00:03:36,660 --> 00:03:38,100
Master has a notorious reputation,

70
00:03:38,100 --> 00:03:39,360
tyrannical and lustful.

71
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:41,200
Could it be that he is after my beauty,

72
00:03:41,200 --> 00:03:43,160
wanting me to be his dual cultivation cauldron?

73
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:46,160
But although Master has lived for thousands of years,

74
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,000
he looks very young

75
00:03:48,500 --> 00:03:50,160
and exceptionally handsome.

76
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,160
He is also a Quasi-Emperor of this era,

77
00:03:52,160 --> 00:03:54,030
and so overbearing and protective.

78
00:03:54,030 --> 00:03:55,460
Being his cauldron

79
00:03:55,700 --> 00:03:57,860
doesn't seem to be a loss.

80
00:03:59,300 --> 00:04:01,430
Naturally, I did a divination

81
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:03,660
and found out we are destined.

82
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,300
The way she looks at me

83
00:04:05,300 --> 00:04:06,600
is getting weirder and weirder.

84
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:09,660
Could she be thinking of rebelling against her master?

85
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:12,200
If I hadn't lived a second life,

86
00:04:12,200 --> 00:04:14,400
I would have almost believed your nonsense.

87
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:17,060
If Master really asks me to sleep with him later,

88
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,899
what should I do to seem more reserved?

89
00:04:20,660 --> 00:04:22,300
If I agree directly,

90
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:24,490
will I seem lacking in self-respect?

91
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:26,660
But if I refuse...

92
00:04:28,230 --> 00:04:28,960
Qingchen,

93
00:04:29,730 --> 00:04:30,260
you...

94
00:04:31,860 --> 00:04:33,159
I am willing!

95
00:04:35,360 --> 00:04:37,220
I haven't even said what it is yet.

96
00:04:42,100 --> 00:04:45,700
Ding! Disciple Ji Qingchen's affection has greatly increased.

97
00:04:45,960 --> 00:04:48,260
Gained 300 Destiny Fortune Points.

98
00:04:49,100 --> 00:04:49,900
Yao'er,

99
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:53,830
the future of Taixuan Holy Land depends entirely on you.

100
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:55,560
Don't worry, Master.

101
00:04:55,659 --> 00:04:57,400
I will not let you down.

102
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:00,260
This is...

103
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,260
Master, what is this?

104
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:06,260
This is the resonance mark of an ancient bloodline.

105
00:05:06,260 --> 00:05:06,900
Yao'er,

106
00:05:07,400 --> 00:05:09,460
it should be the hidden grand clan behind you.

107
00:05:09,460 --> 00:05:11,460
A mighty figure has come to find you.

108
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:12,830
Clansmen?

109
00:05:12,930 --> 00:05:13,630
Hahaha!

110
00:05:13,830 --> 00:05:14,360
I knew it!

111
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,300
My judgment is absolutely correct.

112
00:05:16,300 --> 00:05:17,930
Yao'er has an astonishing background.

113
00:05:17,930 --> 00:05:18,660
By following her,

114
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:23,400
our Taixuan Holy Land will surely rise to the top.
